A shopping cart checkout application
====================================

The application provides checkout pricing functionality for a basic shopping cart.
The shopping cart is a case insensitive, comma separated list of oranges and apples.
Other item types are simply ignored.

It is called via the following url: e.g http://localhost:9000/price/orange,apple,Apple .

Controllers
===========

- Checkout.scala:

  The application controller handling the url requests making use of a pricing component

Components
==========

- Pricer.scala:

  Pricing component.



